                  ʾabbā
               </foaf:name><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>He was a monk of medieval time born in Tamben where he built 42 churches.
                  His life is known from his Gadla Yoḥanni za-Dabra ʿAśā. He was born from a mother 
                  who was a wife of a certain  
                     šum
                    
                  of Tamben. Additional information of him is also evoked in a number of 
                  hymnological compositions.</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><snap:occupation>abbot</snap:occupation></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10428Yohanni"><snap:hasBond rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/bond/AllianceWith-https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1886Ammoni"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/bond/AllianceWith-https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1886Ammoni"><rdf:type rdf:resource="http://data.snapdrgn.net/ontology/snap#AllianceWith"/><snap:bond-with rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1886Ammoni"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10428Yohanni"><ecrm:P129i_is_subject_of rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1521GadlaY"/></rdf:Description><oa:Annotation rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10428Yohanni/place/annotation/1"><oa:hasTarget rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10428Yohanni"/><oa:hasBody rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC5882Tamben"/><oa:annotatedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2026-04-05+02:00</oa:annotatedAt><lawd:hasName>Tamben</lawd:hasName></oa:Annotation><oa:Annotation rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10428Yohanni/place/annotation/2"><oa:hasTarget rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10428Yohanni"/><oa:hasBody rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC5882Tamben"/><oa:annotatedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2026-04-05+02:00</oa:annotatedAt><lawd:hasName>Tamben</lawd:hasName></oa:Annotation><oa:Annotation rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10428Yohanni/person/annotation/1"><oa:hasTarget rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10428Yohanni"/><oa:hasBody rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10428Yohanni"/><oa:annotatedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2026-04-05+02:00</oa:annotatedAt><betmas:hasRole><betmas:Role><betmas:roleType rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/title"/><betmas:rol